CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh courier newspaper, December 9, 1972, pg. 9 reads: "More Visiting Guests - Looking well pleased over a most enjoyable evening are these additional out-of-town guests. From left to right: Mr. and Mrs. William Teamor, Mr. and Mrs. Frank S. Brown (guests of Atty. and Mrs. Joseph Givens), Mr. and Mrs. John H. Meyers, Mrs. Clara Atwell, Carl Atwell, Mrs. Bertha Garnett, all of Steelton, Pa., and Betty and Clay Harvey."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Mrs. Teamor, William Teamor, Mrs. Brown, Frank S. Brown, Mrs. Meyers, John H. Meyers, Clara Atwell, Carl Atwell, Bertha Garnett, Betty Harvey, and Clay Harvey, posed for Urban League Guild of Pittsburgh dinner dance, in Allegheny Club, Three Rivers Stadium
